──[ Projects ]──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────[ 2026 ]

    Here is what I am building right now.

──[ Petrodata.ar ]─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────[ Active ]

    A data platform for Argentina's oil, gas, minerals, and rare-earth
    sectors. Production data for 76+ operators, 50+ mineral projects,
    11 O&G provinces. Backend: NestJS + Payload CMS + Neon PostgreSQL.
    Frontend: Next.js. Dark theme, Bloomberg-meets-Linear data density.

    https://petroldata.ar

──[ Lex Pulse ]─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────[ Active ]

    A daily legal newsletter + website + job board for Argentina's legal
    sector. Federal scope (not just Buenos Aires). Expanding to Córdoba,
    Santa Fe, Mendoza. Database of court rulings, regulatory updates,
    and legal-sector job listings.

──[ TenderClaw ]────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────[ Active ]

    Government tender scraping and monitoring platform. Multi-channel
    GTM: cold email, LLM SEO, paid ads, directories, Show HN, Stripe
    integration. Grey/black hat approach.

──[ Nini ]───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────[ Active ]

    AI assistant framework. Multi-agent architecture with persona-based
    interaction, prompt tuning, evaluation harness, and sandbox testing.
    Spanish-language reports with English prompt engineering.

──[ AIGrou ]─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────[ 2023 ]

    AI agent platform for agricultural management. Won Seedstars LATAM
    x World Economic Forum. Presented at GIZ (Germany) and WEF (Mexico).
    Applied data-driven AI to real-world operations for small and medium
    landowners.

──[ W3G ]────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────[ 2025 ]

    Fullstack mobile app (React Native, TypeScript, Node.js, Zustand).
    Promoted from engineer to product manager. Lead a team of 3, own
    roadmap, sprint planning, and delivery.

──[ DeFi Zoo / VaultEdge ]──────────────────────────────────────────────────[ 2024 ]

    DeFi lending/vault product. React/TypeScript frontend, Node.js
    microservices, Wagmi/Viem/Ethers onchain integration. Event-driven
    subgraphs for blockchain data ingestion. Automated liquidations.

──[ Num Finance → Twin Finance ]─────────────────────────────────────────────[ 2023 ]

    Cross-border stablecoin payments. USD/FX-pegged assets across
    Argentina, Brazil, Mexico. Pix-to-stablecoin settlement. SQL
    analytics dashboards for supply, liquidity, and product KPIs.

──[ Mangos Wallet ]──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────[ 2022 ]

    Consumer wallet for underbanked users in emerging markets.
    Web2-style social auth over AA (account abstraction,
    ERC-4337). Yield-bearing protocol integration (AAVE).
    Ownership over key architecture and technical decisions.

